<main role="main" class="bg-light">
  <section class="jumbotron-home text-center">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="jumbotron-heading text-intense">Experiment.rocks</h1>
      <p class="lead text-muted">Discover your happiest life - one experiment at a time</p>
      <p>
        <a href="<%= categories_path %>" class="btn btn-primary my-2">View experiments</a>
        <% unless current_user.present? %>
          <a href="<%= new_user_registration_path %>" class="btn btn-secondary my-2">Register</a>
        <% end %>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="container">

    <hr class="featurette-divider_home mt-0">

    <div class="row justify-content-between">
      <div class="col-md-6 experiment-steps">
        <h2 class="text-intense">Get started</h2>
        <div class="step">
          <h2 class="text-intense text-brand h4">1. Choose an experiment</h2>
          <p class="">
            Browse the experiments per category to find out how they might improve your life.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="step mt-4">
          <h2 class="text-intense text-brand h4">2. Track the impact it has on your life</h2>
          <p class="">Fill in a baseline survey before you start, and track your progress on a day to day basis. </p>
        </div>

        <div class="step mt-4">
          <h2 class="text-intense text-brand h4">3. Evaluate the results after 3 weeks</h2>
          <p class="">Fill in the ending survey and see the results in your charts. </p>
        </div>

        <div class="step mt-4">
          <h2 class="text-intense text-brand h4">4. Celebrate & Repeat</h2>
          <p class="">Congratulations! You tried something new and found out whether it improved your life. Whenever you're ready, try out a new experiment! </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-4 mt-4 mt-sm-0">
        <h2 class="text-intense">About</h2>
        <div class="about text-center">
          <img src="https://s3.eu-central-1.amazonaws.com/experiment.rocks/marlies_avatar.jpg" alt="Marlies, author of experiment.rocks">
          <p class="mt-3">
          Hi! Iâ€™ve spent countless hours researching happiness and mindfulness and trying out what I learned. <br><br>
          On this site, you'll find the experiments that made the most impact in my life, plus experiments that I'm excited to try out.<br><br>
          Join in and start discovering your happiest life too!<br><br>
          Marlies
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="featurette-divider_home">
  </div>
</main>
